data.description: Welcome home to this three-bedroom, two-bathroom house with great curb appeal near Texas Tech University. Located on a corner lot, it offers a warm and inviting atmosphere highlighted by a cozy fireplace. Perfect for both relaxation and entertaining, the thoughtful layout ensures comfort in every room. Call and set up your private tour today!
